OL,3,C'I can play a dead body': How the
OL,4,CQueen inspired a crime novel
OL,6,FBestselling author Peter James says
OL,7,Fthe basis for his latest fictional
OL,8,Fcrime thriller, 'The Hawk Is Dead',
OL,9,Fwas suggested by the Queen.
OL,11,FHe explains: "A senior member of the
OL,12,Froyal household said, 'You know Her
OL,13,FMajesty wrote to you about setting it
OL,14,Fin London, actually she'd like you to
OL,15,Fset a novel in Buckingham Palace with
OL,16,Fa few murders'.
