OL,3,C'I can play a dead body': How the
OL,4,CQueen inspired a crime novel
OL,6,F"I discovered ten years ago that Queen
OL,7,FCamilla is a massive fan ... she said
OL,8,FI was one of her two favourite
OL,9,Fauthors, the other was Jane Austen, so
OL,10,FI'll take that."
OL,12,FThe Queen is a passionate advocate for
OL,13,Freading and gave Peter special
OL,14,Fpermission to research his story, in
OL,15,Fwhich she becomes a central character.
