OL,3,C'I can play a dead body': How the
OL,4,CQueen inspired a crime novel
OL,6,FThe author adds: "She has been
OL,7,Fbrilliantly helpful, I was given
OL,8,Fcomplete access to Buckingham Palace.
OL,9,FThere's a big chase scene in the book
OL,10,Fand I had a three-and-a-half-hour tour
OL,11,Fto get it right. I love the fact that
OL,12,Fshe's such a fan of books."
OL,14,FThe novel opens with the royal train
OL,15,Fderailing and brings fictional
OL,16,Fdetective Roy Grace into the heart of
OL,17,Fthe Monarch's power, Buckingham
OL,18,FPalace, as he is called to solve what
OL,19,Fappears to be an assassination attempt.
