OL,3,C'I can play a dead body': How the
OL,4,CQueen inspired a crime novel
OL,6,FPeter describes: "I saw Queen Camilla
OL,7,Fwhen she was in Jersey last July and
OL,8,Fshe said, 'How's the book coming
OL,9,Falong?'.
OL,11,F"I said, 'Well, Your Majesty, I've got
OL,12,Fyou being quite heroic, helping
OL,13,Feveryone off a wrecked train', and she
OL,14,Fsaid, 'I don't know if I would be that
OL,15,Fheroic'.
OL,17,F"What people don't know is that senior
OL,18,Fmembers of the Royal Family, including
OL,19,Fthe King and Queen, are trained in
OL,20,Fself-defence, so you don't want to
OL,21,Fmess with her."
