OL,3,C'I can play a dead body': How the
OL,4,CQueen inspired a crime novel
OL,6,FThe Queen has also been on set to see
OL,7,Fhow the books are retold in the ITV
OL,8,Fdrama series Grace, starring John
OL,9,FSimm, and even lightheartedly
OL,10,Fsuggested having a part in front of
OL,11,Fthe camera.
OL,13,FPeter says: "I did say to her,
OL,14,F'Perhaps you'd like to be an extra?'
OL,15,Fand she said, 'Maybe I can be a dead
OL,16,Fbody'. She's got a wicked sense of
OL,17,Fhumour and is huge fun."
