OL,3,C'I can play a dead body': How the
OL,4,CQueen inspired a crime novel
OL,6,FPeter gave the Queen a final draft
OL,7,Fcopy of the novel and says he was
OL,8,Fconcerned about what her reaction
OL,9,Fmight be.
OL,11,FHe adds: "I was terrified because I
OL,12,Fput real words into their mouths, I
OL,13,Fhad a lot of help from the household
OL,14,Fbut I didn't sleep the night before. I
OL,15,Fthought she was going to come up to me
OL,16,Fand say, 'It's terrible, you can't
OL,17,Fpublish it'.
