OL,3,C'I can play a dead body': How the
OL,4,CQueen inspired a crime novel
OL,6,F"She walked in, came over with a big
OL,7,Fsmile and said, 'I absolutely love
OL,8,Fit'. I asked if there was anything she
OL,9,Fwanted to change and she said, 'Not
OL,10,Fone word'. It was amazing, one of the
OL,11,Fbest moments of my life."
